data.description: 3 CAR GARAGE - MOUNTAIN VIEW - SOUTH PATIO.  This home offers plenty of storage and a lot of room for family/friends and entertaining.    Upstairs is a ''spacious casita'' with a Jack and Jill bath for your guests.  Large Primary Bedroom and office/guest bedroom downstairs.   Garage offers plenty of room for 2 cars, golf cart (or side-by-side) and bicycles.  Kitchen opens to family room w/views of the Catalina Mtns.  New composite sink & faucet in kitchen. Dining room fits a large round table - great when entertaining!   Mstr Bdrm has TWO walk-in closets. View of Mtns from Mstr Bdrm. Back patio offers view, privacy and wonderful shade!  Enjoy both a lovely sunrise and  beautiful sunset from this south patio.  Lush landscaping front and back.  All you need to do is add your personal touch.
